public static final class Calendar.Instances
extends Object
implements BaseColumns, Calendar.EventsColumns, Calendar.CalendarsColumns

Contains one entry per calendar event instance. Recurring events show up every time they occur.

Constant Field Values

SORT_CALENDAR_VIEW

public static final String SORT_CALENDAR_VIEW
The sort order is: events with an earlier start time occur first and if the start times are the same, then events with a later end time occur first. The later end time is ordered first so that long-running events in the calendar views appear first. If the start and end times of two events are the same then we sort alphabetically on the title. This isn't required for correctness, it just adds a nice touch.
